Isu tinopa yakasanganiswa MBR yekurasa tsvina michina ine PVDF mhango fiber membrane zviyero, ayo anoshandiswa zvakanyanya kurapa maindasitiri uye matunhu emakanzura, zvakaita sewewage kubva kuzvipatara, mahotera, misha, mataundi, nzvimbo dzekudzidzisa, nzvimbo dzinoyevedza zvichingodaro.  Imwe fekitori iri iripo in Liaoning dunhu uye imwe iri Dunhu reJiangxi. Isu tine anopfuura makore gumi nematanhatu 'ruzivo muMBR kurapwa kwemvura yakasviba. We inopa kurapwa kweseweji, kuisirwa, kubvunza, kuvimbisa, kuyedza uye kugadzirisa kuona kuramba kuchitevedza. Tiri kutsvaga boka rekunze kwekuchengetedzwa kwezvakatipoteredza uye indasitiri yekurapa mvura yakasviba vanhu vakakurumbira mukudyidzana kwakabatana.
